.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, orange, light-blue, brown, chestnut
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, pakistani, turkish, italian, canadian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, lemonade, hot-chocolate, 7up
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: azuremaster, bongani, baccarat, oliveros, davidoff
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldgoat, pony, goat, ferret
1. the argentine is the person who likes light-blue
2. the swedish is the owner of the pony
3. the pakistani is the person drinking hot-chocolate
4. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes brown
5. the person who likes orange is the person drinking sprite
6. the baccarat-smoker is the owner of the goldgoat
7. the person who likes chestnut is the bongani-smoker
8. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle
9. the italian is on the far left
10. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit
11. the owner of the ferrets is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker
12. the azuremaster-smoker is the person drinking cola
13. the turkish is the oliveros-smoker
14. the italian is on the left or right of the person who likes azure
15. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    chestnut	|     azure	|      light-blue	|     orange	|     brown	|
| Nationality	|   italian	|    pakistani	|    argentine	|    turkish	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     rabbit	|    ferret	|     goldgoat	|     goat	|      pony	|
| Beverage	|    7up	|     hot-chocolate	|     lemonade	|    sprite	|      cola	|
| Cigar		|   bongani	|    davidoff	|  baccarat	|    oliveros	|   azuremaster	|
